{"tid":1624002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成立臨時警隊比臨時政府重要","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:22.000Z","uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56d1a9fb36400590c0266a7a1b704767e9db0b39","tid":1624002,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得左 <br />\n五大訴求<br />\n我地無要求過港獨 只要求雙普選<br />\n美國出到聲係維持一國兩制 非港獨<br />\n臨時政府暫時未係適當時機<br />\n<br />\n我地首要既係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 制裁呢三萬人</span></span><br />\n臨時警隊或重組警隊可以在政府各部門借人<br />\n亦都支持白警 公開同事既惡行證據<br />\n雖然無一個白警 呢一刻全部狗都抵死 比盡你灰警<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">篤灰警</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁做 <br />\n對市民可以滿足到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對灰警 將上層罪行公布 重制後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你可以連升幾級</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對政府可以合法地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借用中共武警/解放軍力量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對美國 可以合法地監察，協助<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提供武力支援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到雙普選成功，訴求成功<br />\n就可以立法方式停止武警解放軍借兵<br />\n<br />\n緊急法 暫停警隊職務<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成立臨時警隊</span>"},{"pid":"e6186eb1b0405695b3f2929926ac9ce4911b1e2f","tid":1624002,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7419af2c79d5638f660303bbf0c8783575332905","tid":1624002,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:47:03.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"35e38bc0e757a144a736041327ac0138e688e82c","tid":1624002,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"裝修後班蝻同藍絲趁火打劫，都要人挷起佢同拍低佢"},{"pid":"9b792a2ff37fb553264b5820b3d9e355a6dbd425","tid":1624002,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04f6f71e8794ebc82ce24e974c4193f14394724d","tid":1624002,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"臨時警隊美國唔會反啦掛"},{"pid":"419f8f1073ea0e5b9d60ec80ed940fe704fc3999","tid":1624002,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:02:47.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"eb39e512b4c6b9402f5325b7930cfbcb7803ff06","tid":1624002,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"臨時警隊<br />\n多方有利"},{"pid":"05e9d12d52bd884cd0d49ff506fc511afba29422","tid":1624002,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5848f589bbd4b58b6dced7759b6c4006bdf3a78","tid":1624002,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fabd56f8ee8ac89e9fc9b787c57e52a67b3a20","tid":1624002,"uid":291476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"民間自衛隊都講左好幾個月 都無左件事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}